webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/WP-HA-6-leb-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\">In this series, we take you from bare-metal to a highly-available WordPress site, load-balanced over two nodes and resistant to VPS failures using MariaDB multi-master replication, DRBD, and round-robin DNS.</p><p>In this, the final episode of the series, we enable round-robin DNS and test our setup. What happens if we take down node #1? What about node taking down node #2? Does the user\u2019s browser correctly switch nodes? Find out as we put our work to the test!</p><p>This video is based on our <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/highly-available-wordpress-from-scratch-part-6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">earlier tutorial</a>.</p><p>Earlier videos in this series:</p><ul><li style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9knkrFRmLIk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Part 1</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uXSZpXp2wnk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Part 2</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/nlzGO_LXsgw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Part 3</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=__4ldzkwdp8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Part 4</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0hRGcxMkLPs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Part 5</a></li></ul></li></ul><p><iframe data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GIcitL273QE?feature=oembed\" title=\"Building a Highly Available WordPress Site, Part 6: Does It Work?!?\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" data-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GIcitL273QE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></iframe></p><hr><p>We would appreciate your likes, shares, and above all subscriptions on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/